&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 398px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Repair or replace mechanism and fittings faults including lifting mechanisms, recliners and electrical components.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;width: 102.102px;&quot;&gt;
