&lt;h3&gt;Maths and English requirements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;English and maths qualifications must be completed in line with the apprenticeship funding rules.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Duration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Typically this apprenticeship will take 24 months to complete.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Review date&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After 3 years.&lt;/p&gt;
